snippet.title: Disney Fairies:TinkerBell DS Game Trailer
snippet.description: Trailer for the new Disney Fairies:TinkerBell DS game,the game will be released with TinkerBell on DVD and Blu-Ray which will introduce the Disney Fairies franchise and will let us hear TinkerBell talking for the first time.
